{"article_id":"UGgeqxQtWXPVlgXj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell broke with President-elect Donald Trump over Russia on Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"he supports a congressional investigation into findings","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that Russian hackers attempted to influence the election .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"McConnell praised the American intelligence community ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"he has `` the highest confidence in the intelligence community , and especially the Central Intelligence Agency ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"-- which Trump had recently lambasted over its findings .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"McConnell 's comments were an implicit rebuke of Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"who has questioned","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"whether Russia actually interfered with the election ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"including with hacks of Democratic operatives .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"A bipartisan group of senators","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"-- John McCain , R-Arizona , Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer , Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-South Carolina , and Sen. Jack Reed , D-Rhode Island --","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"had on Sunday called for an investigation into the intelligence community 's finding","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that Russia attempted to influence the election .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"The President-elect on Sunday morning blasted the intelligence community anew ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"calling its assessment","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"that Russia interfered in the election","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"`` ridiculous . '","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"' `` I think","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"it 's just another excuse .","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"I do n't believe it , ''","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said in an interview on `` Fox News Sunday . '' McCain ,","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"who has called for an investigation into the hacking ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"told CNN 's Jake Tapper Monday on `` The Lead ''","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"his own 2008 presidential campaign was hacked by the Russians .","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"`` The key to this is to try to find out what the Russians ' intentions were .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"Were they intending to change the outcome of our election ?","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"If so ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"it 's more serious , ''","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"McCain said .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"`` Let me just speak for myself :","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"The Russians are not our friends , ''","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"McConnell , a Kentucky Republican , told reporters at a Monday morning news conference .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"we ought to approach all of these issues on the assumption","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"the Russians do not wish us well , ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wisconsin , took the same position as McConnell .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` Any foreign intervention in our elections is entirely unacceptable , ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Ryan said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` And any intervention by Russia is especially problematic","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"because , under President Putin , Russia has been an aggressor","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that consistently undermines American interests . ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Two days earlier Trump sided with Russia over the CIA","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and attacked the US intelligence assessment of Russia 's role .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` These are the same people","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that said","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Saddam Hussein had weapons of mass destruction , ''","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Trump 's transition team said in a terse , unsigned statement","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"targeting the CIA","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"on Friday .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Though he supported calls for an investigation into Russian hacking ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"McConnell poured cold water on the idea","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"-- which McCain had proposed --","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"of a select committee","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to investigate Russian hacking .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Ryan , too , said","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"the House Intelligence Committee ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"which has investigated cyberhacking ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"would handle the matter","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"-- rejecting Democrats ' calls for a bipartisan joint committee .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Trump , meanwhile , continued dismissing intelligence reports Monday morning ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"tweeting ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"`` Unless you catch `` hackers '' in the act ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"it is very hard to determine who was doing the hacking .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Why was n't this brought up before election ? ''","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Ignoring the conclusions of the intelligence community","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that Russia sought to meddle in the US election","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"is dangerous ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Sen. Angus King said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"The Maine independent ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"who caucuses with the Democrats in the Senate","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and sits on the Senate Intelligence Committee ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"told CNN 's Chris Cuomo on `` New Day '' on Monday","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that what Director of National Intelligence James Clapper tells you , `` you can take it to the bank . ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"`` If you blow off what Jim Clapper 's telling you ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"you do so at your peril , ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"King said .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Clapper is a retired lieutenant general with decades of intelligence experience across administrations of both parties ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"King pointed out .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"ODNI pulls together intelligence from all of the US government 's intelligence agencies .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Clapper 's office , along with the Department of Homeland Security , put out a statement in October","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"declaring","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"that the US government and intelligence had concluded","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that senior levels of the Russian government had directed the hacking of Democratic political groups in the US and release of information from them with the intent","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"of influencing the US election .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"A series of leaks of emails and internal documents from the Democratic National Committee and Hillary Clinton 's campaign chairman over the weeks and months","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"leading up to the election","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"jolted the race ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"vexing Democrats","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and resulting in the resignation of officials from the DNC","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"including its former chairwoman .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Republicans did not suffer the same release .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"The Russia involvement has been a point of contention , however .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Despite overwhelming consensus between the private sector and intelligence community","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that Moscow was directing the attacks","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and involved in the leaks ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Trump has continually denied","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that Russia played a role ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"saying over the weekend","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"he does n't believe the conclusion .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"The latest dust-up has come over a report from The Washington Post","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that the CIA has concluded","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Russia did n't just seek to sow discord in the election ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"but actually sought to get Trump elected ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"following an earlier report by CNN .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"King said","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"while questions remain about the Moscow 's intention ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"there 's little doubt about Moscow 's involvement .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"( Trump ) ought to sit down with some of the top people ...","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and take a deep breath","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"and listen to this , ''","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"King said .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"he 's too defensive right now ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"and I can understand that .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"This is serious business ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"but you know","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"this is not a partisan issue . ''","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"King also supported the efforts of his colleagues McCain , Schumer , Graham and Reed","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"to hold bipartisan hearings on the topic .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"McCain and Schumer appeared together on `` CBS This Morning ''","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"to discuss the need for the hearings .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"They , too , agreed","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the evidence is clear","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Russia engaged in hacking ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"though the intentions are still under question .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"`` I ca n't reach that conclusion yet ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"which is why we need a bipartisan effort","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"to uncover the whole situation , ''","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"McCain said .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"`` It 's another form of warfare","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and the entire issue is going to be examined by the Armed Services Committee","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"because it 's a threat to our national security . ''","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Schumer said","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"the seriousness of the situation calls for a bipartisan approach","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"that does n't devolve into politics .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"`` We need to get to the bottom of this in a fair , nonpartisan , non-finger pointing way , ''","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"`` This is something","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"that should unite Republicans , Democrats , conservatives , liberals , patriots . ''","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"The White House strongly suggested Monday","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"that Trump was the beneficiary of Russian meddling in the US election ,","depth":4},{"id":147,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"it was the President-elect","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"who praised Vladimir Putin on the campaign trail .","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"`` The emails","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"that had been hacked and leaked by the Russians ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"these were emails from the DNC and John Podesta , not from the RNC and Stephen Bannon , ''","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"said White House Press Secretary Josh Earnest .","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"`` It was the President-elect","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"who over the course of the campaign indicated","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"that he thought","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"that President Putin was a strong leader , ''","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"Earnest added .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":160,"text":"members of Congress should `` spare us the hand-wringing ''","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"and move forward with investigating Russian ties to the election .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":323,"left":0,"right":322,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":322,"left":305,"right":321,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":229,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":173,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":169,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":165,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":1,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":2,"right":163,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":5,"right":167,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":6,"right":166,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":9,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":10,"right":170,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":223,"right":227,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":205,"right":222,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":199,"right":204,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":192,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":176,"right":191,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":174,"right":175,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":